-*- text -*-

* Configure option: use one single owner setting (default, settable
  by root?) or info for the current user

* Show owner/user photo, optionally

* Use vCard. Example (address fields might be wrong order):

    BEGIN:VCARD                             
    VERSION:2.1				   
    REV:20020725T161606Z			   
    UID:0				   
    FN:Thomas Stephens			   
    N:Stephens;Thomas			   
    ADR;HOME:;address;city;state;zip;country
    ADR;WORK:				   
    TEL;WORK:555-1234			   
    X-Qtopia-Gender:0			   
    END:VCARD                               

